---
description: MirrorWorks Smart FactoryOS design system. Apply to ALL React component creation, styling, and UI modification.
globs: ["src/**/*.tsx", "src/**/*.css", "src/components/**/*"]
---

## 1. Colours

MW Yellow (brand accent — 10% of UI):
- `mw-yellow-50`: #FFFBF0 — selected row bg, subtle highlight
- `mw-yellow-100`: #FFF3D6 — text selection highlight
- `mw-yellow-200`: #FFE8AD — warning alert border
- `mw-yellow-300`: #FFDB7A
- `mw-yellow-400`: #FFCF4B — **primary CTA**, active states, checked controls
- `mw-yellow-500`: #F2BF30 — hover on primary
- `mw-yellow-600`: #E6A600 — active/pressed on primary
- `mw-yellow-700`: #CC8E00
- `mw-yellow-800`: #A67300
- `mw-yellow-900`: #805900

Grey scale (30% structure):
- Near Black `#0A0A0A` — headlines, primary text, active icons
- Dark `#2C2C2C` — body text, text on yellow buttons
- Mid `#525252` — table body, descriptions
- Medium `#737373` — labels, captions, inactive icons (minimum text colour)
- Border `#E5E5E5` — card borders, dividers
- Subtle `#F5F5F5` — page background, input bg
- Warm `#F8F7F4` — grouped card bg inside sheets
- White `#FFFFFF` — card backgrounds (60%)

Neutral scale aliases: `neutral-50` (#FAFAFA) through `neutral-900` (#0A0A0A).

Dark accent: `mw-mirage` #1A2732 — dark variant buttons, dark badges, sidebar bg.
Off-white: `mw-off-white` #F8F7F4.

Status (dots/badges only, never card backgrounds):
- Success: #36B37E
- Info: #0052CC
- Warning: #FACC15
- Error: #DE350B

**Deprecated — do not use**: `mw-earth`, `mw-saddle`, `mw-sea-foam`, `mw-azure`, `mw-ai-purple`.

## 2. Typography

Font stack:
```css
--font-family-sans: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
--font-family-mono: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
```

Roboto weights: 300 (Light), 400 (Regular), 500 (Medium), 700 (Bold), 900 (Black — marketing only).
Roboto Mono weights: 400, 500.

No other fonts. Geist, JetBrains Mono, Inter are all deprecated.

M3 type scale:

| Token | Size | Weight | Line-height | Letter-spacing | MW usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| display-large | 57px | 400 | 64px | -0.25px | Marketing hero stats |
| display-medium | 45px | 400 | 52px | 0px | — |
| display-small | 36px | 400 | 44px | 0px | — |
| headline-large | 32px | 400 | 40px | 0px | Page titles |
| headline-medium | 28px | 400 | 36px | 0px | — |
| headline-small | 24px | 400 | 32px | 0px | Section headers, dialog titles |
| title-large | 22px | 400 | 28px | 0px | Card titles (primary) |
| title-medium | 16px | 500 | 24px | 0.15px | Card titles (secondary), nav |
| title-small | 14px | 500 | 20px | 0.1px | Compact titles, sidebar |
| body-large | 16px | 400 | 24px | 0.5px | Primary body text |
| body-medium | 14px | 400 | 20px | 0.25px | Table body, form content |
| body-small | 12px | 400 | 16px | 0.4px | Captions, timestamps |
| label-large | 14px | 500 | 20px | 0.1px | Button text, active labels |
| label-medium | 12px | 500 | 16px | 0.5px | Column headers, badges |
| label-small | 11px | 500 | 16px | 0.5px | Micro text, version numbers |

Custom: `stat-display` — 48px, weight 400, 56px line-height, -0.25px tracking. Roboto Mono. For KPI cards.

Rules:
- Financial values, currency, totals → Roboto Mono
- Job numbers, IDs, codes → Roboto Mono
- Everything else → Roboto
- Max 3 type sizes per card
- Sentence case everywhere. Only label-medium/label-small uppercase.

## 3. Shape (Border Radius)

| M3 token | Value | CSS var | Tailwind | Default use |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| none | 0px | `--shape-none` | `rounded-none` | Table inner rows |
| extraSmall | 4px | `--shape-xs` | `rounded-[var(--shape-xs)]` | Checkboxes, small chips |
| small | 8px | `--shape-sm` | `rounded-[var(--shape-sm)]` | Toggle tracks, compact elements |
| medium | 12px | `--shape-md` | `rounded-[var(--shape-md)]` | Buttons, inputs, dropdowns |
| large | 16px | `--shape-lg` | `rounded-[var(--shape-lg)]` | Cards, modals, dialogs |
| extraLarge | 24px | `--shape-xl` | `rounded-[var(--shape-xl)]` | Bottom sheets, expanded containers |
| full | 9999px | `--shape-full` | `rounded-full` | Badges, pills, avatars |

## 4. Elevation

| Level | M3 dp | CSS var | Tailwind | Use |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 0 | 0dp | `--elevation-0` | `shadow-none` | Page background |
| 1 | 1dp | `--elevation-1` | `shadow-xs` | Content cards |
| 2 | 3dp | `--elevation-2` | `shadow-sm` | Interactive cards |
| 3 | 6dp | `--elevation-3` | `shadow-md` | Popovers, dropdowns |
| 4 | 8dp | `--elevation-4` | `shadow-lg` | Sticky headers, nav |
| 5 | 12dp | `--elevation-5` | `shadow-xl` | Modals, sheets |

Max 3 elevation levels visible on any page. Dark accent cards don't use shadow.

## 5. Touch Targets

| Context | Min height | Class |
|---|---|---|
| Desktop interactive | 48px | `h-12 min-h-[48px]` |
| Shop floor interactive | 56px | `h-14 min-h-[56px]` |
| Primary CTA | 80px | `h-20 min-h-[80px]` |
| Table rows | 56px | `min-h-[56px]` |

## 6. Component Patterns

### Buttons

```tsx
// Primary (yellow)
<Button>Save job</Button>
// → bg-[var(--mw-yellow-400)] text-[#2C2C2C] hover:bg-[var(--mw-yellow-500)]

// Ghost
<Button variant="ghost">Cancel</Button>
// → hover:bg-[var(--neutral-50)]

// Dark
<Button variant="dark">Export</Button>
// → bg-[var(--mw-mirage)] text-white hover:bg-[var(--mw-mirage)]/90

// Large (shop floor)
<Button size="lg">Start production</Button>
// → h-14 min-h-[56px]

// Disabled (M3 split)
<Button disabled>Locked</Button>
// → bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.12] text-[#0A0A0A]/[0.38]
```

### Cards

```tsx
// Flat card (elevation-1)
<Card className="border border-[var(--neutral-200)] shadow-xs rounded-[var(--shape-lg)]">

// Elevated card (elevation-2)
<Card className="border border-[var(--neutral-200)] shadow-sm rounded-[var(--shape-lg)]">

// Dark accent card (no shadow)
<Card className="bg-[var(--mw-mirage)] text-white border-none rounded-[var(--shape-lg)]">
```

### Tables

```tsx
// Table container
<Card className="rounded-[var(--shape-lg)] border border-[var(--neutral-200)]">
  {/* Filter bar */}
  <div className="p-4 border-b border-[var(--neutral-100)] flex gap-3">
    <Input placeholder="Search..." />
  </div>
  <Table>
    <TableHeader>
      <TableRow>
        <TableHead>Job #</TableHead>
      </TableRow>
    </TableHeader>
    <TableBody>
      <TableRow> {/* min-h-[56px] hover:bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.04] even:bg-[var(--neutral-50)] */}
        <TableCell className="font-mono">MW-2024-0891</TableCell>
      </TableRow>
    </TableBody>
  </Table>
</Card>
```

### Progress

```tsx
// Linear
<Progress value={65} />
// Track: bg-[var(--neutral-200)], Fill: bg-[var(--mw-yellow-400)], rounded-full

// Segmented (custom)
<div className="flex gap-1">
  {steps.map((s, i) => (
    <div key={i} className={cn("h-2 flex-1 rounded-full", i <= current ? "bg-[var(--mw-yellow-400)]" : "bg-[var(--neutral-200)]")} />
  ))}
</div>
```

### Frosted Glass (sheets, dialogs, tooltips)

```tsx
// Overlay
className="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm"

// Dialog/Sheet content
className="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-xl rounded-[var(--shape-lg)]"

// Tooltip
className="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md text-foreground border border-white/30 shadow-lg rounded-[var(--shape-md)]"
```

### Badges

```tsx
<Badge>Default</Badge>                    // neutral grey
<Badge variant="accent">Active</Badge>   // MW Yellow
<Badge variant="dark">Admin</Badge>      // Mirage
<Badge variant="success">Complete</Badge>
<Badge variant="destructive">Error</Badge>
<Badge variant="warning">Pending</Badge>
<Badge variant="outline">Draft</Badge>
```

### Avatars

```tsx
<Avatar className="ring-2 ring-white shadow-sm">
  <AvatarImage src={url} />
  <AvatarFallback className="bg-[var(--neutral-100)] text-[var(--neutral-500)] font-medium text-sm">
    MQ
  </AvatarFallback>
</Avatar>
```

## 7. Spacing

- Page padding: `p-8`
- Card padding: `p-6`
- Row gap: `gap-6`
- Section spacing: `space-y-8`
- Grid: 8px base (`gap-2` = 8px)

## 8. State Layers

M3 opacities applied as overlay of the content's own colour:

| State | Opacity | Pattern |
|---|---|---|
| Hover | 8% | `hover:bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.08]` |
| Focus | 10% | `focus:bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.10]` |
| Pressed | 10% | `active:bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.10]` |
| Dragged | 16% | `bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.16]` |

Disabled (split — never blanket opacity):
```tsx
// Light surface
className="disabled:bg-[#0A0A0A]/[0.12] disabled:text-[#0A0A0A]/[0.38]"

// Dark surface
className="disabled:bg-white/[0.12] disabled:text-white/[0.38]"
```

## 9. Motion

### Easing (CSS variables)

| Token | Curve | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--ease-standard` | `cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1.0)` | General transitions |
| `--ease-standard-decelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0, 1)` | Elements entering |
| `--ease-standard-accelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0.3, 0, 1, 1)` | Elements leaving |
| `--ease-emphasized` | `cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1.0)` | Important transitions |
| `--ease-emphasized-decelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1.0)` | Entering with emphasis |
| `--ease-emphasized-accelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0.3, 0, 0.8, 0.15)` | Leaving with emphasis |

### Duration

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--duration-short1` | 50ms | Micro-interactions |
| `--duration-short2` | 100ms | Simple state changes |
| `--duration-medium1` | 250ms | Standard transitions (default) |
| `--duration-medium2` | 350ms | Complex transitions |
| `--duration-long1` | 450ms | Page transitions |
| `--duration-long2` | 550ms | Emphasis transitions |

Default: `duration-[var(--duration-medium1)] ease-[var(--ease-standard)]`.
Enter: `ease-[var(--ease-standard-decelerate)]`.
Exit: `ease-[var(--ease-standard-accelerate)]`.

## 10. Critical Rules

1. Sentence case everywhere (not Title Case)
2. Australian English (colour, organisation, metre, labour)
3. No gradients — flat colours only
4. No decorative borders — borders only for structure
5. Monochromatic icons (Lucide) — no multi-colour icons
6. One primary action per card (one yellow button max)
7. No hover-only interactions on touch surfaces
8. Helpful empty states with illustration + CTA
9. Specific error messages ("Job MW-2024-0891 not found" not "Error occurred")
10. Cmd+K search always available
11. Short forms — avoid full-page wizards
12. ShadCN/Radix components only — no custom UI primitives
13. No Babylon.js in React state — use refs and useEffect
14. Components under 400 lines — split if larger

## 11. Module Notes

- **Make**: 56px+ touch targets, large checkboxes, progress bars for job stages
- **Book**: Roboto Mono for all financial values, right-aligned numbers
- **Sell**: Dark accent cards for pipeline stages, MW Yellow for won deals
- **Plan**: Segmented progress bars for schedule, timeline views
- **Ship**: Timeline component + large checkboxes for dispatch checklists
- **Buy**: Card nesting for PO → line items, three-way match indicators
